      "file_path": "/home/mohammed/.claude/plans/swift-foraging-river.md",
      "content": "# Plan: Daily Opus+BLOX Crypto Research Cron Job\n\n## Context\nThe user runs crypto research using Claude Code's `/crypto_research_haiku` command (and manual opus runs with BLOX focus). They want this automated daily \u2014 specifically the Opus-tier research with BLOX platform analysis, with results committed and pushed to https://github.com/muah1987/crypto.git.\n\n## Approach\n\nCreate a bash script + cron job that:\n1. Runs `claude` CLI in non-interactive (headless) mode with the opus+BLOX research prompt\n2. Copies outputs to the git repo\n3. Commits and pushes to GitHub\n\n### Files to Create\n\n**1. `/home/mohammed/scripts/daily-crypto-research.sh`** \u2014 Main automation script\n- Runs `claude --print` (non-interactive) with a prompt that triggers opus agents with BLOX focus\n- Uses `--model opus` flag for deepest analysis\n- Timestamps the run\n- Copies results to `/home/mohammed/crypto-repo/`\n- Git add, commit, push\n- Logs output to `/home/mohammed/logs/crypto-research.log`\n\n**2. Cron entry** \u2014 Schedule daily at 08:00 Amsterdam time\n```\n0 8 * * * /home/mohammed/scripts/daily-crypto-research.sh >> /home/mohammed/logs/crypto-cron.log 2>&1\n```\n\n### Script Details (`daily-crypto-research.sh`)\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# Daily Opus+BLOX Crypto Research\nTIMESTAMP=$(date +\"%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S\")\nREPO=\"/home/mohammed/crypto-repo\"\nOUTPUT_DIR=\"$REPO/$TIMESTAMP/opus\"\nLOG=\"/home/mohammed/logs/crypto-research-$TIMESTAMP.log\"\n\n# Create directories\nmkdir -p \"$OUTPUT_DIR\"/{crypto_market,crypto_analysis,crypto_macro,crypto_plays}\nmkdir -p /home/mohammed/logs\n\n# Run claude in headless mode with the full opus+BLOX research prompt\nclaude -p \"Run crypto research with opus agents and BLOX platform focus.\nToday's date is $(date +%Y-%m-%d).\n[detailed prompt with 4 opus agent calls + BLOX focus + investable coins summary]\nWrite all outputs to $OUTPUT_DIR/\" \\\n  --model opus \\\n  --max-turns 50 \\\n  >> \"$LOG\" 2>&1\n\n# Git commit and push\ncd \"$REPO\"\ngit add -A\ngit commit -m \"Daily crypto research: $TIMESTAMP (Opus+BLOX)\" \\\n  --author=\"muah1987 <muah1987@users.noreply.github.com>\"\ngit push origin main\n```\n\n### Key Decisions\n- **Timing**: 08:00 CET daily (markets have settled overnight, good snapshot time)\n- **Model**: Opus only (deepest analysis, matches user's request)\n- **BLOX focus**: Hardcoded in prompt for coin analyzer + investment plays agents\n- **Auto-push**: Commits and pushes automatically to GitHub\n- **Logging**: Each run logged separately for debugging\n\n## Verification\n1. Run the script manually: `bash /home/mohammed/scripts/daily-crypto-research.sh`\n2. Check logs: `cat /home/mohammed/logs/crypto-research-*.log`\n3. Verify git push: `cd /home/mohammed/crypto-repo && git log --oneline -5`\n4. Verify cron: `crontab -l`\n"
