      "content": "#!/bin/bash\n#\n# Daily Opus+BLOX Crypto Research\n# Runs at 08:00 CET via cron\n# Outputs to /home/mohammed/crypto-repo/ and pushes to GitHub\n#\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nexport PATH=\"$HOME/.local/bin:$HOME/.nvm/versions/node/$(ls $HOME/.nvm/versions/node/ 2>/dev/null | tail -1)/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:$PATH\"\nexport HOME=\"/home/mohammed\"\nexport TZ=\"Europe/Amsterdam\"\n\nTIMESTAMP=$(date +\"%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S\")\nREPO=\"/home/mohammed/crypto-repo\"\nOUTPUT_DIR=\"$REPO/$TIMESTAMP/opus\"\nLOG=\"/home/mohammed/logs/crypto-research-$TIMESTAMP.log\"\n\necho \"=== Daily Crypto Research Started: $(date) ===\" | tee \"$LOG\"\n\n# Create output directories\nmkdir -p \"$OUTPUT_DIR\"/{crypto_market,crypto_analysis,crypto_macro,crypto_plays}\n\n# Run claude in headless mode with opus+BLOX research\nclaude -p \"You are running an automated daily crypto research job. Today's date is $(date +%Y-%m-%d).\n\nExecute the following 4 opus agent tasks IN PARALLEL:\n\n1. MARKET OVERVIEW: Launch crypto-market-agent-opus to provide a comprehensive real-time cryptocurrency market overview for the Top 20 cryptocurrencies by market cap. Include current prices, 24h changes, market cap, volume, and market dominance. Write the report to $OUTPUT_DIR/crypto_market/crypto-market-agent-opus.md\n\n2. COIN ANALYSIS (BLOX FOCUS): Launch crypto-coin-analyzer-opus to find emerging coins with high growth potential. IMPORTANT: Check the BLOX platform (weareblox.com - Dutch crypto exchange) and their available coins. Identify which BLOX-listed coins are new, emerging, and have growth potential. Also analyze other emerging coins beyond BLOX. For each coin state the ticker, price, and whether it's on BLOX. Write the report to $OUTPUT_DIR/crypto_analysis/crypto-coin-analyzer-opus.md\n\n3. MACRO CORRELATION: Launch macro-crypto-correlation-scanner-opus to analyze correlations between macroeconomic events and crypto market movements. Cover Fed policy, inflation, S&P 500, DXY, and sector impacts. Write the report to $OUTPUT_DIR/crypto_macro/macro-crypto-correlation-scanner-opus.md\n\n4. INVESTMENT PLAYS (BLOX FOCUS): Launch crypto-investment-plays-opus to identify actionable investment opportunities with entry/exit strategies. Focus on coins available on BLOX platform. Include risk scores, targets, and stop losses. Write the report to $OUTPUT_DIR/crypto_plays/crypto-investment-plays-opus.md\n\nAfter all 4 agents complete, create a summary file at $OUTPUT_DIR/investable-new-coins.md listing ONLY the coin names, tickers, prices, BLOX availability, and risk tier in a clean markdown table.\n\nWrite ALL reports using the Write tool. Do NOT use Bash for file writing.\" \\\n  --model opus \\\n  --max-turns 80 \\\n  --allowedTools \"Write,Edit,WebSearch,Bash(date:*),Bash(mkdir:*),Task\" \\\n  >> \"$LOG\" 2>&1\n\necho \"=== Claude research completed: $(date) ===\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\n\n# Count generated files\nFILE_COUNT=$(find \"$OUTPUT_DIR\" -name \"*.md\" -type f | wc -l)\necho \"Generated $FILE_COUNT report files\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\n\n# Git commit and push\ncd \"$REPO\"\ngit add -A\n\nif git diff --cached --quiet; then\n    echo \"No changes to commit\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\nelse\n    git commit -m \"$(cat <<EOF\nDaily crypto research: $TIMESTAMP (Opus+BLOX)\n\nAutomated daily run - $FILE_COUNT reports generated.\nMarket overview, coin analysis (BLOX focus), macro correlations, investment plays.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"\n    git push origin main\n    echo \"=== Pushed to GitHub: $(date) ===\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\nfi\n\necho \"=== Daily Crypto Research Complete: $(date) ===\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\necho \"Output: $OUTPUT_DIR\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\necho \"Log: $LOG\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\n"
    },
